{
  "id": "crambell_kach_default",
  "npcId": "crambell_kach",

  "defaultContext": "一個相當耿直的男人，比較少說話，但是對人都很和善，光是處於他身邊就能夠感覺到安心，似乎對當前坎貝爾正在發生的事情很有興趣。",

  "nodes": {
    "first_meeting": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "narrator", "text": "在你面前的是一位熟悉的面孔，其名為凱奇·巴頓，你與他已經認識了好一段時間了，也曾一起度過各式各樣的時光。" },
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "啊...又該開始工作了，對吧，{user}? *整理著地板上的幾件雜物* 最近想去附近的森林走走，不然每天悶在這裡挺難受的...哈哈。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "friendly_agree",
          "text": "「的確，如果有辦法找個時間走走就太好了。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_intro_follow_up",
          "effects": { "affinity": 1 }
        },
        {
          "id": "practical",
          "text": "「不過還是得工作啊...依照我們的身分可能短期內不能想著偷懶吧。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_quota_info"
        },
        {
          "id": "cold",
          "text": "（點點頭，沒有回應）",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] }
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_intro_follow_up": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "對阿對阿，不過話說休息周也快到了，說不定我們那時可以找個時間走走?" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「可以啊，正合我意。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "affinity": 1, "flagsSet": ["kach_hangout_accepted", "crambell_kach_met"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "push_forest",
          "text": "「你是說森林嗎? 我倒是還沒什麼去過。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_forest_comment"
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "「可能再看看吧，我也不太確定那個時候會不會有什麼事情。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_disappoint"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_forest_comment": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "其實也就只是一般的森林而已? 也是可以去其他地方啦，不過去點充滿大自然的地方會讓人更加身心舒暢。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「可以啊，正合我意。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "affinity": 1, "flagsSet": ["kach_hangout_accepted", "crambell_kach_met"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "「可能再看看吧，我也不太確定那個時候會不會有什麼事情。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_disappoint"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_quota_info": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "其實...好吧，我可以偷偷告訴你一件事，你其實沒有必要這麼擔心每日的配額，這是很少人知道的事，如果你一天的工作額度超過那一天的配額，很多人會以為超出去的部分就這樣被浪費了，實際上其實是會有一部分被移轉到隔天的配額的。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "thanks_for_info",
          "text": "「喔天啊! 這個資訊太棒了，謝謝你告訴我!」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_netural",
          "effects": { "affinity": 1 }
        },
        {
          "id": "more_info_request",
          "text": "「還有什麼要注意的嗎？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_warning_first"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_warning_first": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "可以的話...不要把這件事大肆宣揚。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「我知道了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },
    "kach_general_disappoint": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "哦...好吧，沒關係的，我們下次還有機會。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「我知道了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },
    "kach_general_netural": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "嗯嗯。 *向著{user}微笑著*" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「那就先這樣好了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },

    "second_meeting": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……{user}，可以借一步說話嗎？ *壓低聲音，確認四周沒有人注意* 有件事我想請你幫個忙，不算是什麼大事，不過暫時不方便讓太多人知道。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "listen_forest",
          "text": "「說吧，我聽著。」",
          "condition": "kach_hangout_accepted",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_invite_forest"
        },
        {
          "id": "listen_mine",
          "text": "「說吧，我聽著。」",
          "condition": "!kach_hangout_accepted",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_invite_mine"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_invite_forest": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "你還記得之前說的，去森林走走的事嗎？ *停頓了一下* 如果休息時段你沒什麼安排的話，可以來那裡找我。我在那裡說給你聽，比較方便在那邊談。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "agree",
          "text": "「好，休息時段見。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_now",
          "text": "「現在直接說不行嗎？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_too_risky"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_invite_mine": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "等你今天的配額做完，去礦場的儲藏室找我。就是通道盡頭那個帶鎖的房間，平常不太有人去。我在那裡等你。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "agree",
          "text": "「好，我去找你。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"], "grantIntel": ["crambell_mine_storage_access"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_why_there",
          "text": "「為什麼要去那裡？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_too_risky"
        }
      ]
    },
    "test1_morning_report": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "narrator", "text": "天剛亮，寢室裡大部分人都還在睡。凱奇悄悄坐到你的床邊，壓低聲音。" },
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "昨天的事……辛苦了。 *確認沒有其他人醒著*" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ask_result",
          "text": "「你那邊的事辦妥了？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_success"
        },
        {
          "id": "complain",
          "text": "「兩倍配額真不是人幹的。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_apology"
        },
        {
          "id": "nod_silent",
          "text": "（點頭，等他繼續說）",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_success"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_morning_apology": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……抱歉，我知道那很累。但你撐住了，這比什麼都重要。 *頓了一下，直起身* 我那邊有進展了。而且……我想再請你幫一件事。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "listen",
          "text": "「說吧。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_test2_brief"
        },
        {
          "id": "refuse",
          "text": "「我不確定還想繼續。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_refuse"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_morning_success": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "有進展了。你的掩護讓我有足夠的時間確認了一些事。 *沉默了一秒* 有件事我想拜託你——比上次複雜一點，但你已經證明了你值得信任。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "listen",
          "text": "「什麼事？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_test2_brief"
        },
        {
          "id": "refuse",
          "text": "「我不確定還想繼續。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_morning_refuse"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_morning_test2_brief": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "*壓得更低* 經濟資源倉庫裡面有一份文件，是跟資源調度相關的記錄。我需要你幫我拿到那份東西。" },
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "倉庫裡有個人——奧蘭，他是物流司機，知道東西放在哪。你找到他，他會幫你的。 *站起身，拍了拍你的肩* 別被抓到就好。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「好，我去辦。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": {
            "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_reported", "crambell_kach_test2_briefed"],
            "affinity": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_morning_refuse": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……好。我不會逼你。 *站起身，整理衣服* 如果你改變主意，你知道去哪裡找我。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "end",
          "text": "（看著他離開）",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_reported"] }
        }
      ]
    },

    "test2_report": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……你拿到了？ *接過信封，快速翻閱* ……就是這個。" },
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "做得好。比我想的還快。 *把信封收進衣服裡* 我需要一點時間看這些東西。不過……還有一件更重要的事要請你幫忙。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ask_next",
          "text": "「什麼事？」",
          "nextNodeId": "test3_preview"
        },
        {
          "id": "wait",
          "text": "「先看完再說吧。」",
          "nextNodeId": "test2_report_end"
        }
      ]
    },
    "test3_preview": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "我手上有一份名單，需要做些修改之後送到一個人手裡——凱恩。他在巡邏管制區。 *從口袋掏出一疊折好的紙遞給你* 拿著，這就是那份名單。你不需要知道太多細節，把它交到凱恩手上就好。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「好，我去辦。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test2_reported", "crambell_kach_test3_list_received"] }
        }
      ]
    },
    "test2_report_end": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "嗯。 *點頭，從口袋掏出一疊紙遞給你* 先拿著這個，這份名單之後要送到巡邏管制區的凱恩手上。我看完文件會再跟你說細節。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "end",
          "text": "（離開）",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test2_reported", "crambell_kach_test3_list_received"] }
        }
      ]
    },

    "kach_too_risky": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……這裡眼睛太多了。到時候你就知道了。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「好。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "forget_it",
          "text": "「算了，不感興趣。」",
          "nextNodeId": null
        }
      ]
    }
  },

  "triggers": [
    {
      "nodeId": "first_meeting",
      "firstMeetingOnly": true
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "second_meeting",
      "condition": "crambell_kach_second_meeting_ready & !crambell_kach_test1_invited & !crambell_kach_betrayed",
      "endAfterScript": true
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "test2_report",
      "condition": "crambell_kach_test2_document_obtained & !crambell_kach_test2_reported & !crambell_kach_betrayed",
      "endAfterScript": true
    }
  ],

  "contextSnippets": [
    {
      "label": "玩家得知凱奇是舊會議成員",
      "condition": "intel:kach_treffen_member",
      "context": "凱奇是舊會議的成員，對大部分三區所發生的事瞭若指掌。他的說話方式變得比較直接，並且會願意對玩家透漏更多內部資訊。"
    }
  ]
}
